      "message": "Table 6 contains Table 1. Assuming if Table 1 has 8000 bytes. Then Table 6 can be formed in two ways, logically splitting Table 1 in smaller tables so that Type, Length, Value is preserved or to split Table 1 so that minimum PLDM packets can be generated. In the 2nd case Table 6\u0027s CRC and Padding would only be part of last packet.",
